  "text": "### Vision & Goals  \n• Make user onboarding KYC-compliant without killing conversion  \n  – 80% of users complete KYC in under 5 mins  \n  – Cut manual review queue by at least 60%  \n  – Regional compliance coverage in top 3 markets  \n\n### Must‑Have Features  \n• Front-camera selfie capture w/ liveness check  \n• Upload gov’t-issued ID (passport, DL, etc.)  \n• Name + DOB auto-extract from ID [TODO @Elena]  \n• Manual override panel for compliance reviewers  \n• Local language support for ID types (esp. non-Latin scripts)  \n• Error-handling flow for mismatched fields [TODO @Marco]  \n• Email+SMS fallback if real-time verification fails  \n\n### AI Automation Ideas  \n• “Smart‑ID Verification Bot” flags blurry image uploads + prompts user to re-capture before sending to human reviewer  \n• ML-based “Risk‑Score Predictor” generates probability score (% likelihood of fraud) — Marco to tune thresholding?  \n• All PII processed only in-region; redact unnecessary fields before logging to backend  \n\n### Compliance & Regions  \n• EU – GDPR-compliant storage + AML5 checklist (beneficial ownership, PEPs)  \n• US – FinCEN Customer Due Diligence rule (must flag shell corps)  \n• Indonesia – OJK requires…  \n\n### Open Questions  \n• How might we speed up retries without frustrating legit users?  \n• Should we auto-reject expired IDs or allow grace period?  \n• What’s the fallback if selfie verification fails on low-end devices?",
